%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eways%20to%20manage%20anxiety%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20stress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fceline-dion-always-brings-photos-husband-doctor-stiff-person-syndrome-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718255562000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666a5c05e07904901818860c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fceline-dion-always-brings-photos-husband-doctor-stiff-person-syndrome-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22C%C3%A9line%20Dion%20says%20her%20children%20will%20always%20remind%20her%20to%20bring%20photos%20of%20her%20late%20husband%2C%20Ren%C3%A9%20Ang%C3%A9lil%2C%20along%20whenever%20she%20packs%20for%20a%20trip.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22agoh%40businessinsider.com%20(Amanda%20Goh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fceline-dion-always-brings-photos-husband-doctor-stiff-person-syndrome-2024-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20University%20Body%20Opted%20For%20Biannual%20Admissions%3A%20Explained%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20major%20shift%20from%20traditional%20annual%20admissions%2C%20the%20University%20Grants%20Commission%20(UGC)%20has%20introduced%20a%20policy%20allowing%20universities%20to%20admit%20students%20twice%20a%20year%2C%20specifically%20in%20July%2FAugust%20and%20January%2FFebruary.%20This%20move%20aims%20to%20provide%20universities%20with%20the%20flexibility%20to%20decide%20their%20admission%20cycles%20based%20on%20their%20available%20infrastructure%20and%20faculty.%20However%2C%20adopting%20this%20new%20system%20is%20optional%20for%20universities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECurrent%20System%20And%20Upcoming%20Changes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETraditionally%2C%20students%20are%20admitted%20once%20a%20year%2C%20starting%20in%20July%2FAugust.%20The%20UGC's%20new%20decision%20permits%20universities%20to%20conduct%20admissions%20in%20two%20cycles%20for%20undergraduate%2C%20postgraduate%2C%20and%20PhD%20programmes%3A%20once%20in%20July%2FAugust%20and%20again%20in%20January%2FFebruary.%20This%20approach%20mirrors%20the%20biannual%20admission%20cycles%20of%20some%20international%20universities%2C%20such%20as%20those%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20which%20have%20fall%20and%20spring%20intakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERationale%20And%20Benefits%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UGC%20has%20previously%20implemented%20biannual%20admissions%20for%20open%2C%20distance%20learning%2C%20and%20online%20programmes.%20This%20change%20enabled%20nearly%20half%20a%20million%20students%20to%20enroll%20in%20degree%20programs%20without%20waiting%20for%20an%20entire%20year.%20UGC%20Chairman%20M%20Jagadesh%20Kumar%20explained%20that%20this%20new%20system%20could%20benefit%20students%20who%20miss%20the%20July%2FAugust%20admissions%20due%20to%20health%20issues%2C%20delays%20in%20board%20exam%20results%2C%20or%20personal%20reasons.%20With%20the%20biannual%20admission%20system%2C%20these%20students%20can%20reapply%20in%20January%2FFebruary%20instead%20of%20waiting%20a%20full%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar%20also%20highlighted%20that%20international%20universities%20follow%20a%20biannual%20admission%20system%2C%20which%20could%20enhance%20international%20collaborations%20and%20student%20exchanges%20for%20Indian%20institutions.%20Additionally%2C%20this%20system%20could%20help%20increase%20the%20Gross%20Enrollment%20Ratio%20(GER)%2C%20which%20measures%20the%20ratio%20of%20students%20enrolled%20in%20higher%20education%20to%20the%20eligible%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENext%20Steps%20For%20Institutions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20to%20implement%20biannual%20admissions%20rests%20with%20the%20universities%20themselves%2C%20requiring%20approval%20from%20their%20academic%20and%20executive%20councils.%20Universities%20will%20need%20to%20determine%20which%20programs%20to%20offer%20in%20both%20admission%20cycles%2C%20considering%20the%20availability%20of%20infrastructure%20and%20faculty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUGC%20Chairperson%20Discusses%20Biannual%20Admission%20Process%20In%20Exclusive%20Interview%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV%2C%20UGC%20Chairperson%C2%A0Mamidala%20Jagadesh%20Kumar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20university%20body%20had%20tested%20the%20biannual%20admission%20process%20in%20Online%20and%20Open%20%26amp%3B%20Distance%20Learning%20modes.%20After%20UGC%20permitted%20two-cycle%20admissions%20for%20the%20ODL%20modes%2C%20there%20was%20a%20significant%20rise%20in%20enrollments.%20A%20total%20of%2019%2C73%2C056%20students%20enrolled%20in%20July%202022%2C%20with%20an%20additional%204%2C28%2C854%20students%20in%20January%202023.%20These%20numbers%20show%20that%20a%20second%20academic%20session%20in%20a%20year%20enabled%20nearly%20half%20a%20million%20students%20to%20join%20degree%20programs%20without%20waiting%20a%20full%20academic%20year.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20if%20the%20decision%20was%20made%20with%20all%20stakeholders%20in%20mind%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20biannual%20admission%20system%20is%20a%20global%20practice%3B%20admissions%20are%20conducted%20twice%20a%20year%20at%20all%20global%20universities.%20Only%20in%20our%20country%20is%20it%20done%20once%20a%20year.%20After%20seeing%20the%20positive%20response%20from%20students%20in%20the%20online%20program%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20provide%20a%20similar%20option%20to%20universities%20offering%20physical%20courses.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20mandatory%20requirement%3B%20only%20colleges%20with%20the%20necessary%20infrastructure%20and%20faculty%20can%20opt%20for%20this%20system.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegarding%20aligning%20education%20with%20international%20standards%2C%20Mr.%20Kumar%20explained%2C%20%26quot%3BIncreasing%20the%20Gross%20Enrollment%20Ratio%20(GER)%20is%20a%20national%20requirement%20and%20a%20strong%20recommendation%20of%20the%20NEP%202020.%20Higher%20educational%20institutions%20have%20a%20social%20responsibility%20to%20increase%20student%20intake.%20Conducting%20admissions%20twice%20a%20year%20allows%20universities%20to%20utilize%20available%20infrastructure%20and%20teaching%20faculty%20more%20effectively%2C%20admitting%20more%20students%20and%20helping%20to%20improve%20the%20GER.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718255460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-06%2Fstudents_650x400_61496744807.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fwhy-university-body-opted-for-biannual-admissions-explained-5879533%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20UGC%20has%20previously%20implemented%20biannual%20admissions%20for%20open%2C%20distance%20learning%2C%20and%20online%20programmes.%20This%20change%20enabled%20nearly%20half%20a%20million%20students%20to%20enroll%20in%20degree%20programs%20without%20waiting%20for%20an%20entire%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fwhy-university-body-opted-for-biannual-admissions-explained-5879533%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fwhy-university-body-opted-for-biannual-admissions-explained-5879533%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fwhy-university-body-opted-for-biannual-admissions-explained-5879533%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ATM%20cash%20withdrawals%20to%20cost%20you%20more%3F%20Operators%20seek%20hike%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718254820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110954080%2Cimgsize-45574.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2