Maharashtra's%20Panvel%C2%A0%E2%80%93%20where%20he%20has%20a%20farmhouse%20-%C2%A0armed%20with%20weapons%20sourced%20from%20a%20Pakistani%20arms%20supplier.%C2%A0Jailed%20gangster%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%2C%20along%C2%A0with%C2%A0his%20Canada-based%20cousin%20Anmol%20Bishnoi%20and%20associate%20Goldie%20Brar%2C%20had%20reportedly%20acquired%20AK-47s%2C%20M-16s%2C%20and%20other%20high-calibre%20weapons%20from%20a%20Pakistani%20arms%20dealer.%20The%20plan%20was%20to%20either%20ambush%C2%A0the%20star's%C2%A0car%C2%A0or%20attack%20his%20farmhouse%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718253720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fo6pmfn0g_salman-khan-balcony_625x300_13_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwoke-up-to-gunshots-what-salman-khan-told-cops-about-firing-at-home-5879188%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Actor%20Salman%20Khan%20has%20revealed%20that%20he%20was%20woken%20up%20by%20the%20sound%20of%20gunshots%20on%20April%2014%20when%20two%20bike-borne%20men%20opened%20fire%20outside%20his%20residence%20in%20Mumbai's%20Bandra.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwoke-up-to-gunshots-what-salman-khan-told-cops-about-firing-at-home-5879188%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwoke-up-to-gunshots-what-salman-khan-told-cops-about-firing-at-home-5879188%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwoke-up-to-gunshots-what-salman-khan-told-cops-about-firing-at-home-5879188%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22T20%20WC%3A%20WI%20into%20Super%20Eight%2C%20winless%20NZ%20face%20early%20exit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718253548000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110956681%2Cimgsize-93814.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fspor