onicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Fcatherine-lagaaia-to-star-as-moana-in-live-action-moana-with-dwayne-johnson%2Farticleshow%2F110953693.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Man%2C%2041%2C%20Dies%20On%20Fiji%20Airways%20Flight%2C%20Airline%20Blames%20%26quot%3BMedical%20Condition%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%C2%A0A%2041-year-old%20US%20man%20died%20while%20travelling%20from%20Nadi%2C%20Fiji%20to%20San%20Francisco%20on%20a%20Fiji%20Airways%20flight%20on%20Saturday.%C2%A0Fiji%20Airways%20flight%20FJ780%20was%2090%20minutes%20away%20from%20San%20Francisco%20International%20Airport%20when%20an%20unidentified%2041-year-old%20man%20%26quot%3Bencountered%20a%20medical%20condition%26quot%3B%2C%20according%20to%3Ca%20data-uw-rm-brl%3D%5C%22PR%5C%22%20data-uw-original-href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fijiairways.com%2Fen-us%2Fmedia-centre%2Fstatement-on-incident-aboard-fiji-airways-flight%2F%5C%22%20data-uw-rm-ext-link%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fijiairways.com%2Fen-us%2Fmedia-centre%2Fstatement-on-incident-aboard-fiji-airways-flight%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fijiairways.com%2Fen-us%2Fmedia-centre%2Fstatement-on-incident-aboard-fiji-airways-flight%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C2%A0a%20statement%20from%20Fiji%20Airways%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0The%20cabin%20crew%20and%20a%20doctor%20on%20board%20tried%20to%20save%20the%20man%2C%20but%20he%20did%20not%20survive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20FlightAware%2C%20the%20Airbus%20crew%20announced%20a%20medical%20emergency%20before%20successfully%20landing%20at%20San%20Francisco%20International%20Airport%20at%202%3A34%20p.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Despite%20the%20best%20efforts%20of%20our%20cabin%20crew%20and%20a%20doctor%20on%20board%20who%20provided%20immediate%20assistance%2C%20the%20passenger%20unfortunately%20passed%20away.%20Our%20flight%20crew%20promptly%20declared%20a%20medical%20emergency%2C%20and%20we%20were%20given%20priority%20for%20landing%20by%20the%20SFO%20authorities.%20Fiji%20Airways%20ground%20operations%20and%20the%20relevant%20authorities%20were%20informed%20in%20advance%20and%20were%20prepared%20to%20meet%20the%20aircraft%20upon%20arrival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20flight%20landed%20safely%20in%20San%20Francisco%20a%20short%20while%20ago.%20Our%20thoughts%20and%20heartfelt%20condolences%20go%20out%20to%20the%20family%20and%20friends%20of%20the%20deceased%20during%20this%20difficult%20time%2C''%20the%20statement%20further%20read.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20identity%20of%20the%20passenger%20and%20the%20medical%20condition%20he%20suffered%20aboard%20the%20plane%20have%20not%20been%20released%20by%20the%20airline.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFiji%20Airways%20remains%20committed%20to%20the%20safety%20and%20well-being%20of%20our%20passengers%20and%20crew%2C%20and%20we%20are%20cooperating%20fully%20with%20the%20authorities%20as%20they%20manage%20this%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20airline%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20airline%20also%20offered%20condolences%20to%20the%20man's%20family.%C2%A0''Our%20thoughts%20and%20heartfelt%20condolences%20go%20out%20to%20the%20family%20and%20friends%20of%20the%20deceased%20during%20this%20difficult%20time.%20We%20commend%20our%20cabin%20crew%20and%20the%20assisting%20doctor%20for%20their%20swift%20and%20professional%20response%20to%20this%20emergency%2C''%20Fiji%20Airways%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20February%2C%20a%2063-year-old%20man%20onboard%20a%20Lufthansa%20flight%20from%20Thailand%20to%20Germany%20died%20after%20gushing%20out%20%26quot%3Blitres%20of%20blood%26quot%3B%20from%20his%20mouth%20and%20nose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fman-63-dies-after-blood-gushes-from-his-mouth-nose-mid-flight-on-germany-bound-flight-5029846%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENe