0of%20fertilisers%20and%20pesticides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20soil%20health%20had%20deteriorated%20and%20I%20had%20to%20keep%20using%20growth%20promoters%20to%20ensure%20a%20good%20harvest.%20Over%20the%20past%20three%20years%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20been%20able%20to%20phase%20out%20the%20pesticides%20slowly%2C%20and%20today%2C%20I%20use%20only%20vermicompost.%20My%20costs%20have%20reduced%20while%20my%20production%20and%20soil%20health%20have%20improved%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Kuldeep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20icing%20on%20the%20cake%20is%20that%20Kuldeep%20now%20produces%20his%20own%20vermicompost%2C%20trained%20by%20Yash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmers%20working%20with%20Yash%20start%20by%20making%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F341515%2Fiit-guwahati-organic-vermicompost-for-farmers-fast-biodegradation-technique-ajay-kalamdhad-mati-dhan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evermicompost%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20as%20little%20as%201%2F4th%20of%20an%20acre%2C%20which%20would%20suffice%20for%20their%20own%20use.%20If%20they%20want%20to%20do%20it%20commercially%2C%20they%20would%20need%20at%20least%20one%20to%20two%20acres%20of%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20Fertile%20Beeghas%20has%20transformed%20over%202%2C500%20tonnes%20of%20cattle%20dung%20and%20organic%20waste%20into%20vermicompost%2C%20earning%20an%20income%20of%20Rs%2013.5%20lakh%20in%20the%20last%20two%20months.%20They%E2%80%99ve%20also%20prevented%20the%20burning%20of%20over%20950%20tonnes%20of%20rice%20straws%20from%20100%20acres%20of%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYash%20hopes%20to%20train%20over%2010%2C000%20farmers%20across%20the%20country%20and%20help%20them%20improve%20their%20soil%20health.%20%E2%80%9CFarmers%20are%20the%20torchbearers%20of%20our%20country.%20Just%20like%20we%20give%20importance%20to%20our%20physical%20health%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20time%20to%20devote%20time%20and%20effort%20to%20improving%20the%20health%20of%20o